{"tid":2428762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一日內四人打科興疫苗後送院　39歲男感眩暈顫抖須留醫","createTime":"2021-03-01T19:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T00:38:49.000Z","uid":261647,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"19f3014a0823d35abcc43af4e6f6407de29e3194","tid":2428762,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/一日內四人打科興疫苗後送院-39-歲男感眩暈顫抖須留醫/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-39-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%84%9F%E7%9C%A9%E6%9A%88%E9%A1%AB%E6%8A%96%E9%A0%88%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%2F&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1xYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=1e040810\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%93%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%8C%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2-39-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%84%9F%E7%9C%A9%E6%9A%88%E9%A1%AB%E6%8A%96%E9%A0%88%E7%95%99%E9%86%AB%2F&h=87d845c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/一日內四人打科興疫苗後送院-39-歲男感眩暈顫抖須留醫/</a><br />\n<br />\n疫苗接種計畫上周五展開，政府今晚（3 月 1 日）發稿公佈，今日有 4 人在接種科興疫苗後，分別出現眩暈、身體無力、血壓高、心悸等症徵，需要送院，其中一名 39 歲男子需留醫觀察。<br />\n<br />\n政府過往每日都公佈接種數字，但就沒有交代送院個案，記者今日在記者會多次追問送院個案資料，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始及公務員事務局局長聶德權均未能回應，至晚上終首以新聞稿公佈今日的相關資料。較早前，曾有一名 72 歲男子心悸不適送院，仍然留院；沙田源禾路體育館疫苗接種中心亦曾有一名婆婆接種後不適。"},{"pid":"6129f887ed9d3785d868e1705a994fb7cd54a7b1","tid":2428762,"uid":14958,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:41:09.000Z","msg":"natural selection"},{"pid":"c91ed76f299690726d22f0f720cf4c848a7bb901","tid":2428762,"uid":114186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T19:50:04.000Z","msg":"抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f